author: tabish
msg: Implements a platform independent Reentrant Lock that's interruptible, has try lock methods and allows timed versions of lock and tryLock.  Uses the AbstractQueuedSynchronizer underneath so its fairly trivial to implement.  Allows for both fair and unfair locking policies.
